#: resources.dbk:954
msgid "Each package has several dedicated web pages.  <literal>http://&packages-host;/<replaceable>package-name</replaceable></literal> displays each version of the package available in the various distributions.  Each version links to a page which provides information, including the package description, the dependencies, and package download links."
